<div class="content-h1"><h1>《彦秫权郡大夫相邀昭亭以病酒不果往得所示佳》</h1></div>
<div class="clear"></div>
<div class="place">
</div>
<div class="clear"></div>
<div class="information" id="unifyprompt"><div class="summary" id="anchor" name="anchor"><p>《彦秫权郡大夫相邀昭亭以病酒不果往得所示佳》是由宋代<a href="http://www.baike.com/wiki/%E6%9D%8E%E5%BC%A5" target="_blank">李弥</a>逊所作的<a href="http://www.baike.com/wiki/%E8%AF%97%E8%AF%8D" target="_blank">诗词</a>。</p><span><a action="editsummaryhref" href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="editSummary();return false;">编辑摘要</a></span>
</div></div>
